verses.roman:
mukunda-dāsa, narahari, śrī-raghunandana
khaṇḍa-vāsī cirañjīva, āra sulocana

synonyms: mukunda-dāsa—Mukunda dāsa; narahari—Narahari; śrī-raghunandana—Śrī Raghunandana; khaṇḍa-vāsī—residents of Khaṇḍa; cirañjīva—Cirañjīva; āra—and; sulocana—Sulocana.
translation: "Here are Mukunda dāsa, Narahari, Śrī Raghunandana, Cirañjīva and Sulocana, all residents of Khaṇḍa.
